This project is an original work, released under the MIT License (see LICENSE).

It packages a "rewrite-then-execute" prompt-optimization command as a Claude Code
plugin. The repository structure, governance, and security scaffolding follow the
conventions established in the author's `ultracost` project
(https://github.com/danielkremen818/ultracost); no code was copied from it.

The diagram toolkit in scripts/svgkit.py renders Feather-style icon glyphs
(https://feathericons.com, MIT License) as inline SVG paths.
